The Barovbe family of Ovu and Olomu Delta State announces the passing of their son, father, grandfather, educationist and businessman Chief Johnson Modika Barovbe. The late Barovbe passed-on 27th December 2021.   Constitution review report ready end of February, says…     CITN, ICSAN, others kick against ICAN Amendment Bill     Constitution review report ready end of February, says…   Rites of passage for Chief Barovbe start on 15th of February in Lagos in a night of tributes. He will be interred in Ovu on 25th of Feb.